data.description: Potential, Potential, Potential! Come and see all this charming 5 bedroom Beacon home has to offer. Many beautiful original features such as moldings, floors, staircase and pocket doors between the LR and DR and between 2 of the BRs. The home also includes a walk up third floor for studio, office or additional storage space. There's more: LR, DR, Den, staircase off the kitchen, a front porch AND a side porch. HW floors under carpet. Built in china cabinet in DR w/original woodwork. Just one block to Main St's shops, galleries and restaurante. Close to hiking trails, Metro North and major highways.
